        <figcaption>两架歼轰-7对“敌”前沿指挥所进行打击。（新华社）</figcaption>
        </figure><br><figure>
        <img src="https://media.dwnews.net/dw/Y-WqZPrhu8Fq8hybsRAhA4K-Wxw%3D/320*0/media/images/dw/0f0ffd144515eb884bb03351559903bd.jpg" alt="此次演习投入的新型武器装备占81.6%。（新华社）" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
